NOTICE — Scope of This License

The amiport toolkit — including the POSIX shim libraries (lib/posix-shim,
lib/posix-emu, lib/console-shim, lib/bsdsocket-shim), build system,
toolchain scripts, website, and all supporting infrastructure — is the
original work of Duncan MacKinnon and is licensed under the MIT License above.

Individual ported programs in ports/*/original/ retain their upstream licenses
(BSD, ISC, MIT, Lucent Public License). The transformed source in
ports/*/ported/ is a derivative work of both the upstream code and the amiport
toolkit. See each port's source file headers and .readme file for upstream
license details.

If you use the amiport shim libraries, build pipeline, or any other part of
the toolkit in your own projects, attribution to amiport and Duncan MacKinnon
is required per the MIT License terms above.
